    'faq_3_title' => 'What is cryptocurrency staking?',
    'faq_3_text' => 'What is cryptocurrency staking? How does it work? What are the benefits of staking cryptocurrency? Get a quick rundown of everything you need to know about staking in this article.',
    'faq_3_btn' => 'Read more',
    'faq_4_title' => 'What is crypto saving?',
    'faq_4_text' => 'With our new service “Crypto saving”, you can easily set up a savings plan based on dollar cost averaging, perfect for long-term investment in cryptocurrency.',
