    'privacy__title' => 'Privacy policy',
    'privacy__nav_title' => 'Content',
    'privacy__introduction_title' => '1. Introduction',
    'privacy__introduction_text' => 'This privacy policy describes how your personal information is collected and processed when using CapitureX, and your rights related to the processing of your personal information. CapitureX is owned and operated by CapitureX Enterprises Limited, registered in the Philippines. In this statement, CapitureX Enterprises Limited will be referred to as "CapitureX", or "we". CapitureX is subject to Philippine law and will process your personal information in accordance with the current privacy legislation.',
    'privacy__data_controller_title' => '2. Data controller',
    'privacy__data_controller_text1' => 'CapitureX is the data controller for your personal information. The data controller is the one who determines the purpose of processing personal information and the processes to be used. The data controller has the ultimate responsibility to ensure that all processing and handling of personal data is in accordance with applicable legislation.',
    'privacy__data_controller_text2' => 'Our full details are: Full name of legal entity: CapitureX Enterprises Limited Registered in the Philippines Contact person: Trang Hoang',
    'privacy__data_controller_text3' => 'Postal address: Manila, Philippines',
    'privacy__data_controller_text4' => 'If you have questions regarding how we collect and use your data, you can contact us using the contact details above.',
    'privacy__data_controller_text5' => 'We wish to have the information we hold about you accurate and up to date. Please let us know if your personal information changes by updating your user profile.',
    'privacy__collect_reason_title' => '3. What personal information we collect and reason for processing',
    'privacy__collect_reason_text1' => 'When you use our website, create a user profile or contact CapitureX, we will process personal information about you. We collect and use your personal information for different purposes. CapitureX’s processing of personal data is subject to your consent or other legal requirements.',
